{"tid":1726556,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"要點樣先算選舉活動?","createTime":"2019-11-16T08:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:15:57.000Z","uid":303805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"43b60444957c927d3f232c8c6e562fe6b48b2501","tid":1726556,"uid":303805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"作為選民好驚有人投訴某D所謂非選舉活動其實係有拉票效果<br />\n利申唔識但想大家研究下, 唔知大家幫下人手拉票會唔會變選舉活動?<br />\n<br />\n例如用以下方式拉票：<br />\n(a) 與選民講話；<br />\n(b) 以微笑、招手、點頭或握手等方式向選民打招<br />\n呼 ；<br />\n(c) 呼喊口號、候選人的名稱或號碼，又或任何呼籲<br />\n的信息；<br />\n(d) 唱歌或唱誦；或<br />\n(e) 向選民打手勢或以信號示意。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/pdf/distco/2019dc/guideline/ch/dc_app4.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fpdf%2Fdistco%2F2019dc%2Fguideline%2Fch%2Fdc_app4.pdf&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXpqf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=d57d8397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/pdf/distco/2019dc/guideline/ch/dc_app4.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}